OL,3,CArsonist who disguised himself with
OL,4,Cblonde wig jailed for 'revenge attack'
OL,6,FAn arsonist who disguised himself by
OL,7,Fwearing a blonde wig as he burned down
OL,8,Fhis old restaurant in a "revenge
OL,9,Fattack" has been jailed.
OL,11,FFakhrul Islam torched the Seventy One
OL,12,FIndian on Breck Road in Poulton in the
OL,13,Fearly hours of 8 December 2024,
OL,14,Fcausing "extensive damage" to the
OL,15,Fbuilding and shutting the business
OL,16,Fdown for more than a year.
