OL,4,Cblonde wig jailed for 'revenge attack'
OL,6,FThe restaurant, which Islam previously
OL,7,Fworked at, was closed at the time, but
OL,8,Fstaff members and a family living
OL,9,Fupstairs had to be rescued from the
OL,10,Fbuilding.
OL,12,FIslam initially denied being
OL,13,Fresponsible for the fire and instead
OL,14,Fclaimed he was driving around as part
OL,15,Fof his work as a taxi driver, but
OL,16,Fpolice were able to track his
OL,17,Fmovements on the night through CCTV
OL,18,Ffootage.
