OL,3,CArsonist who disguised himself with
OL,4,Cblonde wig jailed for 'revenge attack'
OL,6,FThe former restaurant boss was seen
OL,7,Fwalking through Poulton wearing a
OL,8,Fblonde wig as a disguise.
OL,10,FIslam pleaded guilty to arson in the
OL,11,Fface of the evidence compiled by the
OL,12,Finvestigation team.
OL,14,FThe 37-year-old, of Hemingway,
OL,15,FBlackpool was sentenced at Preston
OL,16,FCrown Court earlier this week to seven
OL,17,Fyears and six months in prison.
