OL,6,FDuring sentencing, the Judge described
OL,7,Fthe incident as a revenge attack
OL,8,Fmotivated from ill-feeling between
OL,9,FIslam and the restaurant's new owners.
OL,11,FDet Con Alexa Taylor, of Blackpool
OL,12,FCID, said: "I welcome this sentence
OL,13,Fwhich reflects the gravity and
OL,14,Freckless disregard for life that Islam
OL,15,Fshowed that morning when he carried
OL,16,Fout this arson attack.
